 & =h\boldsymbol{r_{2}} &  & =-a\boldsymbol{r_{1}}-\left(\frac{h}{2}\right)\boldsymbol{r_{2}} &  & =a\boldsymbol{r_{1}}-\left(\frac{h}{2}\right)\boldsymbol{r_{2}}
