\end_inset

 by assumption.
 We therefore seek admissible solutions of 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
\frac{1}{3}\left(\lambda_{2}\left(-\sqrt{3}\sin\theta-\cos\theta\right)\cos\theta+\lambda_{1}\left(-\sin\theta+\sqrt{3}\cos\theta\right)\sin\theta\right) & \geq0\\
